rows.label: soul06_P0101
rows.name:
I'll get the jump on 'em!
Attack up close!

rows.label: soul06_P0102
rows.name:
Let's go! Show them
no mercy!

rows.label: soul06_P0103
rows.name:
You ready? Close in
and nail 'em down!

rows.label: soul06_P0201
rows.name: Open fire! Follow me!

rows.label: soul06_P0202
rows.name:
I'll lay down some fire!
Back me up!

rows.label: soul06_P0203
rows.name: Cripple 'em! We can win this!

rows.label: soul06_P0301
rows.name:
First in, first to win!
Attack up close!

rows.label: soul06_P0302
rows.name:
I'll kick this off.
Lay down some fire!

rows.label: soul06_P0303
rows.name:
Now's your chance!
Use an aura!

rows.label: soul06_P0401
rows.name: Damn... I need healing!

rows.label: soul06_P0402
rows.name:
Let's turn this around.
Buff me up!

rows.label: soul06_P0403
rows.name:
I can't get a break.
Pump me up!

rows.label: soul06_P0501
rows.name: Oh crap. Heal me! Hurry!

rows.label: soul06_P0502
rows.name:
I'm cutting it close.
How 'bout some help here?

rows.label: soul06_P0503
rows.name:
Forget about me.
Just buff up and win this!

rows.label: soul06_P0601
rows.name:
Leave me!
Just take down our foe!

rows.label: soul06_P0602
rows.name:
I'm done for.
Just keep shooting...

rows.label: soul06_P0603
rows.name:
It's all you now.
Aura up!

rows.label: soul06_P0701
rows.name: Yes! Now get in close!

rows.label: soul06_P0702
rows.name:
Excellent!
Now blast them open!

rows.label: soul06_P0703
rows.name: You see that? Cripple 'em!

rows.label: soul06_P0801
rows.name: I got it! Now push in!

rows.label: soul06_P0802
rows.name:
They didn't see THAT coming!
Gun 'em down!

rows.label: soul06_P0803
rows.name:
There we go.
Cripple that freak!

rows.label: soul06_P0901
rows.name: Don't let up! Keep firing!

rows.label: soul06_P0902
rows.name:
Don't get cocky!
We gotta toughen up!

rows.label: soul06_P0903
rows.name:
Focus your attacks!
Go into Overclock!

rows.label: soul06_P1001
rows.name: Now! Close in and clean up!

rows.label: soul06_P1002
rows.name: Fire! They're all yours!

rows.label: soul06_P1003
rows.name:
Yes! Now take the
fight out of 'em!

rows.label: soul06_P1101
rows.name:
Easy now...
Play it safe with an aura!

rows.label: soul06_P1102
rows.name:
Slow down!
Use an aura!

rows.label: soul06_P1103
rows.name: Aura ready! Buff us up!

rows.label: soul06_P1201
rows.name: Time to put it in OVERCLOCK!

rows.label: soul06_P1202
rows.name:
Follow me!
Engaging Overclock!

rows.label: soul06_P1203
rows.name:
Break out an aura!
I'm going into Overclock!

rows.label: soul06_C0101
rows.name:
Who's next? None dare
stand against us!

rows.label: soul06_C0102
rows.name:
Keep shooting! Don't stop
until victory is ours!

rows.label: soul06_C0103
rows.name:
There's still more.
Time to buff up!

rows.label: soul06_C0201
rows.name:
You can't hit me!
Hey, use an aura!

rows.label: soul06_C0202
rows.name:
Not even close.
It's time to power up!

rows.label: soul06_C0203
rows.name:
I'm untouchable!
Now open fire!

rows.label: soul06_C0301
rows.name: I'm on a roll. Smash 'em!

rows.label: soul06_C0302
rows.name: Yeah, baby! Light 'em up!

rows.label: soul06_C0303
rows.name: Hit 'em where it hurts!

rows.label: soul06_C0401
rows.name:
This weather bodes ill.
Use a buff!

rows.label: soul06_C0402
rows.name:
This weather could tank
our strategy. Use an aura!

rows.label: soul06_C0403
rows.name:
They've gotta deal with it too.
Weaken 'em!

rows.label: soul06_C0501
rows.name:
Crank me up!
My legs are run out!

rows.label: soul06_C0502
rows.name:
Who's lightning now?
Buff me up!

rows.label: soul06_C0503
rows.name:
Only thing faster than me
is an Overclock!

rows.label: soul06_C0601
rows.name:
Thanks, man!
Let's bring it in close!

rows.label: soul06_C0602
rows.name:
Much appreciated.
Now attack from range!

rows.label: soul06_C0603
rows.name: I'll be okay. Use an aura!

rows.label: soul06_C0701
rows.name:
Thanks! Keep those
boosts coming!

rows.label: soul06_C0702
rows.name: Good timing. More of that!

rows.label: soul06_C0703
rows.name:
I owe you. Don't forget
to use an aura!

rows.label: soul06_C0801
rows.name: It's not over! Follow me!

rows.label: soul06_C0802
rows.name:
I'm just getting started.
Concentrate your fire!

rows.label: soul06_C0803
rows.name:
I'm not afraid to die.
Just worry about yourself!

rows.label: soul06_C0901
rows.name:
Here's a good spot.
Open fire!

rows.label: soul06_C0902
rows.name:
Keep firing!
I'll cover you from above!

rows.label: soul06_C0903
rows.name:
I'm in position.
You know what to do!

rows.label: soul06_C1001
rows.name:
Down you go!
Now move in, everyone!

rows.label: soul06_C1002
rows.name: Blast 'em! Before they get up!

rows.label: soul06_C1003
rows.name:
Weaken 'em before they rise!
We got this!

rows.label: soul06_C1101
rows.name: They're stunned! Close in!

rows.label: soul06_C1102
rows.name:
Perfect! Talk about
your sitting ducks!

rows.label: soul06_C1103
rows.name:
We could move in,
but I say cripple 'em!

rows.label: soul06_C1201
rows.name: Nighty-night! Now move in!

rows.label: soul06_C1202
rows.name: They're asleep! Light 'em up!

rows.label: soul06_C1203
rows.name:
Target's asleep.
It's now or never!

rows.label: soul06_C1301
rows.name:
I'll hold 'em!
Move in and strike!

rows.label: soul06_C1302
rows.name: Got 'em! Now fire away!

rows.label: soul06_C1303
rows.name: Get in close while I hold 'em!

rows.label: soul06_C1401
rows.name:
My Doll's damaged!
Anybody got a fix?

rows.label: soul06_C1402
rows.name:
Minor damage.
Keep attacking!

rows.label: soul06_C1403
rows.name:
Oh yeah?
Open up on this freak!

rows.label: soul06_C1501
rows.name:
Dammit! Heal up
and fight back!

rows.label: soul06_C1502
rows.name:
Give me a buff so I can turn
this mess around!

rows.label: soul06_C1503
rows.name:
Now you asked for it.
Strike back with Overclock!

rows.label: soul06_C1601
rows.name: Low fuel... I could use a buff!

rows.label: soul06_C1602
rows.name:
I'm running out of fuel!
Do something!

rows.label: soul06_C1603
rows.name: No! I need more fuel!
